| ShortSummary = Elliot has a new plan to destroy backup files at Steel Mountain involving hacking into their climate control system, but this requires physical access. Elliot, Romero, Mobley, and Mr. Robot go to Steel Mountain. Elliot suffers from withdrawal attacks and has multiple hallucinations. Darlene and Trenton stay behind to contact Cisco (her ex) and arrange a simultaneous hacker attack by the Dark Army on Evil Corp's backup sites in China. Meanwhile, Angela and Shayla do [[MDMA|ecstasy]]  which results in the two making out. The next morning, Angela sabotages Allsafe using Ollie's work ID and computer.
